      107.42,
      141.18,
      517.18,
      171.67
    ],
    "text": "Midigama Police Station \u2013 33 Foreign Nationals Arrested on Suspicion of Computer-Related Offences",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      186.13,
      504.97,
      227.01
    ],
    "text": "On the night of 11 May 2026, officers attached to the Midigama Police Station conducted a raid at a tourist hotel in the Pinwatta area within the Midigama Police Division and arrested 33 foreign nationals who were residing at the location.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      241.6,
      510.75,
      268.68
    ],
    "text": "The arrested individuals include 28 Indian nationals and 5 Nepalese nationals, aged between 25 and 35 years.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      283.24,
      515.82,
      324.12
    ],
    "text": "They were taken into custody on suspicion of overstaying without valid visas, engaging in employment while holding tourist visas, possessing duty-free cigarettes, and committing offences under the Computer Crimes Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      338.56,
      436.06,
      351.84
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Midigama Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
